---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="experience" eyebrow="Experience" heading="Where I work">
  <div class="max-w-2xl rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface p-6 sm:p-8">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">Senior Security Analyst</h3>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-fg">Critical Start</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted-fg">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Triage, investigate, contain, and escalate threats across 2,500+
        multi-tenant customer environments
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Work daily across multiple SIEM and EDR/XDR platforms, including
        Microsoft Defender and Sentinel, CrowdStrike Falcon, Cortex XDR/XSIAM,
        SentinelOne, and Splunk
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Tune detection logic to cut alert noise at scale without losing signal
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Section>
